xlogin for Debian
=================

Required Preperation
--------------------

The user must have a .xinitrc script in their home directory.
You can symlink this file to /etc/X11/xinit/xinitrc if you wish.

Usage
-----

To enable automatic login at boot execute:
# systemctl enable xlogin@<username>

Note
----

Using this program bypasses your login password decreasing your device's security.
